data.description: Brand new 2023 metal roof! The kitchen includes a spacious pantry, allowing you to store a variety of food items and kitchen supplies conveniently. The interior of the home features vaulted ceilings, creating an open and spacious atmosphere. There's a bay window in the kitchen area, with a cozy nook where you can enjoy meals while basking in natural light. The master bedroom boasts vaulted ceilings as well, enhancing the sense of space and luxury in the room. The master bathroom includes a jetted tub, providing a luxurious and relaxing space for unwinding and self-care. The yard is enclosed by a fence, which offers privacy while also defining the property's boundaries. The patio is enclosed with screens, allowing you to enjoy the outdoor space while keeping out insects. The property boasts a substantial yard area that has enough space to accommodate a pool, providing ample room for outdoor recreation and relaxation. The outdoor space designated for cookouts and barbecues, perfect for entertaining guests and enjoying outdoor dining. Enjoy breathtaking views of the Choctawhatchee Bay from your dining table or front porch swing. This one-of-a-kind home is nestled in the picturesque Indian Bay subdivision, where Spanish moss hangs from large oak tress offering shade and charm. The neighborhood features a boardwalk through scenic wetlands leading to a community dock, where you can fish, kayak, paddle board, watch for dolphins, and enjoy stunning Florida sunsets. Convenient distance to shopping and a short drive to the beautiful sugar sand beaches of 30A and Destin!
